Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.05,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP Start
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:20.09,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I put together dried up words...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:28.83,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but all I want to do is convey\N my simple feelings to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:34.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The faint wind that blew from that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:38.40,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I threw it away in yesterday's ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:44.55,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So I can live today with you with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:52.19,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But still, this incident will\N continue to trouble you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.08,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's why it must be a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:01:04.12,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now we just try to understand\N each other until nothing remains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:11.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And eventually, we will realize\N that it was everything to us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:18.01,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Sadness will run down our cheeks,\N creating a river of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:28.97,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,1700)}Trembling thoughts will become a strong\N whirl and melt together into one
Comment: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:30.04,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your objective...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:07.19,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\pos(522,697)}Impenetrable Formation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already four o'clock\Nin the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That Fifth Hokage is\Na real slave driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She ought to retrieve\Nthe documents she forgot herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.88,0:02:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll catch cold if you sleep\Nin a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifth Hokage! You were asleep\Njust now, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When you made us\Ngo to fetch the documents!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And only you got to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, Lady Hokage,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,there's something\NI want to report to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Haruno Sakura,\Nit appears that there's no mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...\NThat they should already be on the move...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to getting what I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I will completely\Ndestroy Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So what that pervert wants...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Uchiha 's powers, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumo! Kotetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's somebody\NI want you to bring here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and eat, Shikamaru!\NYour Dad's mission starts today, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not that much time\Nfor morning training!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One OK is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nag, nag, nag from early\Nin the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who it could be\Nso early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you marry\Na hard-edged woman like Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though Mom's like that,\Nshe smiles gently sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the only reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A messenger of the Fifth Hokage\Nis here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uchiha Sasuke apparently slipped out\Nof the village late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And... there is almost no mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that he is headed for\Nthe Village Hidden in the Sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Slipped out?! Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he was enticed by\Nthat Orochimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does Sasuke have to be enticed\Nby a risky guy like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason doesn't matter.\NIn any case, there's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You will perform your first mission\Nas a Chunin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So all I have to do\Nis bring Sasuke back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as there aren't\Nany enemies around,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that shouldn't be\Ntoo much of a hassle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Y es... However, not only is time\Nof the essence on this mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but it may turn into something\Nquite difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a strong possibility that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,those under the control of Orochimaru\Nare guiding Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is turning into a real pain\Nin the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy... I held him in high respect\Nin so many different ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, please give me\Na four-man team
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,composed only of Jonin and Chunin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I can't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You already know\Nthe answer to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, only the barest minimum\Nnumber of Jonin have been left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and the others have all\Nleft the village on missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the next 30 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to gather all the Genin you\Nconsider the best, and leave this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a drag but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the guy,\Nso I just can't just let the matter go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall be, shall be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one guy\NI want to recommend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What! You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You are such a drag starting\Nso early in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But why this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, just wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll change my clothes immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you have your eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,on any other guys besides me\Nwho are excellent?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You said excellent guys, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato chips?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're barbecued meat flavor...\Nyou help out too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it is just potato chips,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let anybody else have\Nthe last piece, no matter who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Choji and I have worked as\Na team for many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so coordinating with him\Nis easiest for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but in this kind of situation,\None would normally solicit Shino first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fat chance...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shino is on a special mission\Nwith his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. He's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Sounds interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it was worth getting up early\Nand going for a walk, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru, what about the other guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take my time to look for some,\Nbut we're pressed for time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't find anybody else\Nby the time we leave the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be just us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that your operation\Nwas a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay for you\Nto be released already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told that I would be able\Nto undertake light training soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hassle,\Nbut the more people the better...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... At a time like this, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Lee! Do what you need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll climb these steps alone\Nstarting tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lee...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine! You go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at our time limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've assembled five people...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Everybody, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to be the squad leader.\NThough it sure is a drag...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think everything will be okay\Nif things are left in your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem very reliable...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with you acting\Nlike the boss, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Although being ordered about by\Nsome unmotivated guy like Shikamaru
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't sit right with me either...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But Shikamaru is already a Chunin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to follow his orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What that means is that\Nthe elders of the village recognized him
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,as capable of being a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that's the case,\Ncome up with some strategy and plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I heard,\Nthere are enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's a strong possibility\Nthat they're gonna ambush us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For a start,\Nas this is a rescue operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we will be in the position\Nof pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nthe enemy can easily gain the initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I will decide\Non a deployment formation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that will respond quickly\Nto any assault by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ignore me and\Nmove of your own accord,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we will all die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We will go in a single file formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all,\Nthe all-important spearhead will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiba, that's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Akamaru go on\Nwalks year round
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and are therefore well-versed in the terrain\Nand geography of the Land of Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And since your nose is\Nvery sensitive,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you can track Sasuke\Nwith your sense of smell and,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you can distinguish booby traps\Nthat carry the enemy's scent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,which makes them\Neasy to find...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And moreover, you and Akamaru as\Na pair will be extremely efficient
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in compensating for the weakness\Nof a single file formation to assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And... second in line will be me,\Nthe squad leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give orders\Nas required in any situation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,from my position\Ndirectly behind Kiba
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and can give orders to those behind me\Nusing only hand signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the middle...\Nin the number three position is Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The middle position is\Nthe best for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,since you're capable\Nof executing quick moves
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and are able to respond immediately\Nto anything in front or behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the cornerstone...\NAnd you have Shadow Clone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And fourth in line is Choji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You. You don't have speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but your ability to strike is the best\Namong the squad members.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Line leader Kiba, I, and Naruto\Nwill launch a surprise attack
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll use you to launch\Nthe deciding blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, your role is\Nto attack the routed enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, on the tail end\Nwill be you, Neji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You are assigned to\Nthe most difficult position of rear lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You will use your Byakugan\Nto constantly check
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that there are no loopholes\Nin the ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? Take a careful look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this diagram to verify\Nthe radius of your assigned watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiba watches the front,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm responsible for\Na wide forward view,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto watches left, Choji right,\Nand Neji...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Using your Byakugan,\Nyou cover the entire area to the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to familiarize myself\Nwith our current military potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me check all the Ninja equipment\Neach of you currently has...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I will commit that\Nto memory straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he just assembled\Nhis men a short while ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,he's already created\Nthe best possible formation...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If not, I want to tell you\Nthe most important thing last.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke and I aren't close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I don't particularly like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he is also a Shinobi belonging\Nto the Village Hidden in the Leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I will put my life\Non the line to help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way\Nof the Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, even I can't just sit back\Nand be a sluggard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I am responsible\Nfor your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... You're acting kind of\Nlike a Chunin, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, as soon as he's checked\Nour Ninja tools, we'll depart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, take out your Ninja tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke wouldn't fall victim\Nto that kind of guy's enticement...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already\Na really powerful guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so he wouldn't need to do\Nthat kind of thing! I guarantee it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... Why, Sasuke...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the whole story\Nfrom Lady Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I can't take you along\Non this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you weren't able\Nto convince Sasuke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All that can be done now is for us\Nto use force to convince him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, your role in this has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, Sakura,\Nthat you and Sasuke...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto... This is a...\Nonce in a lifetime request...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bring...\Nplease bring Sasuke back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do it!\NI wasn't able to stop Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, the only person\Nwho would be able to stop Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,who would be able to save him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is you... Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You like Sasuke so much,\Ndon't you, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand to my very core
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,how painful it must be\Nfor you right now, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, there's one thing\NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel about... Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thwarting someone's love seems\Nto have become natural to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He actually seems to be enjoying\Nmy suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto doesn't understand\Nthe least thing about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto... thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:19:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring Sasuke back without fail!\NI promise that on my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You always understood me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You always helped me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think you're gonna be okay\Nsaying that kind of thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! I will not go back on my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Way of the Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost a little time...\NLet's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:20:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto struck the pose of\Na nice guy as he said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll all be all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm positive...\NI'm positive that it will all go well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Sasuke... Around here will do,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already exited\Nthe Village Hidden in the Leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru has given us\None important task...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So... what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be necessary for you\Nto die once...
